videos.headline: McQueen races for fast-break layup
videos.description: Georgia Tech's Lotta-Maj Lahtinen capitalizes off of South Carolina's miss and tosses ahead to Loyal McQueen for the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (McQueen races for fast-break layup)  2021/3/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: McQueen hyped after beating the buzzer with a side-step 3
videos.description: Loyal McQueen sprints up the court and nails a huge 3-pointer to cut into Georgia Tech's deficit heading into halftime.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (McQueen hyped after beating the buzzer with a side-step 3) 2021/3/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Boston fights through contact for and-1
videos.description: South Carolina's Aliyah Boston muscles past her defender for the bucket, plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Boston fights through contact for and-1) 2021/3/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Boston's jumper seals the Gamecocks' trip to the Elite Eight
videos.description: Destanni Henderson dribbles out of the trap and finds Aliyah Boston for a midrange jumper to help South Carolina advance to the Elite Eight.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Boston's jumper seals the Gamecocks' trip to the Elite Eight) 2021/3/28 ESHEET
